jimmy vestvood : amerikan hero is a 2016 comedy film directed by jonathan kesselman and written by maz jobrani and amir ohebsion .   the films stars maz jobrani , john heard , deanna russo , sheila vand and marshall manesh .   the plot follows an iranian who wins the green card lottery and moves to los angeles with his mom to pursue his dream of becoming an american hero .   the film premiered in limited release in united states on may 13 , 2016 , and has grossed approximately $ 216,000 .